<number box="[700,749,1730,1754]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.24">1.24</number>
wide and posterior 
<number box="[980,1029,1730,1754]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.21">1.21</number>
wide. Palp yellow (
<figureCitation box="[1262,1423,1729,1754]" captionStart="FIGURES 174 – 179. S" captionStartId="34.[151,264,1773,1796]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,551,1752]" captionTargetId="figure@34.[151,1436,551,1752]" captionTargetPageId="34" captionText="FIGURES 174 – 179. S. pterodactyla sp. nov. 174 male, dorsal view; 175 left male palp, ventral view; 176 same, retrolateral view. S. sciosciae sp. nov. 177 male, dorsal view; 178 left male palp, ventral view; arrows point bifid dorsal embolic apophysis; 179 same, retrolateral view. Scale bar = 1 mm (174, 177); 0.25 mm (175 – 176, 178 – 179)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/249780/files/figure.png" pageId="36" pageNumber="187">
Figs 
<number box="[1321,1423,1730,1754]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="178.5" valueMax="179.0" valueMin="178.0">178‒179</number>
</figureCitation>
); triangular RvTA, low ITA; embolus oblique with developed dorsal portion and forked DEA. Legs 
<number box="[1283,1342,1766,1790]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1432.0">1432</number>
, yellow. Length of femur: I 
<number box="[373,425,1802,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.87">1.87</number>
, II 
<number box="[465,517,1801,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="0.95">0.95</number>
, III 
<number box="[567,618,1802,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.03">1.03</number>
, IV 
<number box="[670,722,1802,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.38">1.38</number>
; patella + tibia: I 
<number box="[929,981,1801,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="2.59">2.59</number>
, II 
<number box="[1021,1072,1802,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.33">1.33</number>
, III 
<number box="[1123,1175,1802,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.2">1.20</number>
, IV 
<number box="[1226,1278,1801,1826]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.57">1.57</number>
; metatarsus + tarsus: I 
<number box="[253,304,1837,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.63">1.63</number>
, II 
<number box="[348,400,1837,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="0.96">0.96</number>
, III 
<number box="[453,505,1838,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.22">1.22</number>
, IV 
<number box="[559,611,1837,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="1.57">1.57</number>
. Spination on ventral tibia I: 
<number box="[956,971,1838,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="2.0">2</number>
- 
<number box="[980,995,1838,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="2.0">2</number>
- 
<number box="[1004,1019,1838,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="2.0">2</number>
- 
<number box="[1028,1043,1838,1862]" pageId="36" pageNumber="187" value="2.0">2</number>
