<figureCitation box="[989,1087,1873,1898]" captionStart="FIGURES 174 – 179. S" captionStartId="34.[151,264,1773,1796]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,551,1752]" captionTargetId="figure@34.[151,1436,551,1752]" captionTargetPageId="34" captionText="FIGURES 174 – 179. S. pterodactyla sp. nov. 174 male, dorsal view; 175 left male palp, ventral view; 176 same, retrolateral view. S. sciosciae sp. nov. 177 male, dorsal view; 178 left male palp, ventral view; arrows point bifid dorsal embolic apophysis; 179 same, retrolateral view. Scale bar = 1 mm (174, 177); 0.25 mm (175 – 176, 178 – 179)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/249780/files/figure.png" pageId="36" pageNumber="187">
